data.text:
RELEASE DATE:

4/07/09

DESCRIPTION:

As one half of the A-Team (with Aceyalone), one third of Haiku D'Etat (with Aceyalone and Myka 9), and front man of his group Abstract Tribe Unique (ATU), Ab Rude has endeared himself to fans worldwide through consistent touring and genre defining albums such as 1999's "South Central Thynk Taynk". "Rejuvenation" is a hard hitting soulful ride showcasing Ab Rude's distinct and unlimited vocal stylings. Produced by Vitamin D (G-Unit, Redman, Gift Of Gab, Choklate, Lifesavas, etc.)

Featured emcees include Aceyalone, Myka 9, Sahtyre, Alpha MC, Busdriver, Nocando, Open Mike and Dumbfoundead.
